    "publisher_change_notes": "The GfK Consumer Confidence Barometer is now published by NielsenIQ (NIQ) under permalinks at nielseniq.com/global/en/news-center/<year>/. Across the July 2024 – April 2026 range covered here every monthly release sits on the NielsenIQ news-center, but the press releases continue to be branded 'GfK Consumer Confidence Barometer powered by NIM' and the headline methodology (overall index combining Personal Financial Situation past/next 12 months, General Economic Situation past/next 12 months, and Major Purchase Index) is preserved unchanged from the GfK era. The August 2024 release does not have an indexable NielsenIQ permalink (the slug appears to have been removed/renamed); a tertiary writeup citing the NielsenIQ press release of 2024-08-23 is used for that month, with all other months citing the NielsenIQ permalink directly.",
